==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adamite
<hw>Ad"am*ite</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<ets>Adam</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A descendant of Adam; a human
being.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld> <def>One of a sect of
visionaries, who, professing to imitate the state of Adam, discarded the
use of dress in their assemblies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adam's apple</ent>⟦br⟧
